Categories: animal protagonist, comedy, dub, music, original work, sanrio, slice of...
body:
Aggressive Retsuko

Aggretsuko

Rating: 3/3

Categories: animal protagonist, comedy, dub, music, original work, sanrio, slice of life, work life

Red panda office worker who goes to karaoke bars to sing death metal about the annoyances of everyday life. Relatable asf. The first season may seem daunting but each episode is only a minute long so it won’t even take two hours to complete.

S1, 100 eps (sub only)

ONA, 10 eps

We Wish You a Metal Christmas, 1 ep

ONA S2, 10 eps

summary: Oh boye. well i guess its the end game Lets keep the routine alive and this is the 2018 art summary! since i wont be able to...
caption:
Oh boye. well i guess its the end game


Lets keep the routine alive and this is the 2018 art summary! since i wont be able to doodle for like atleast a month or 3 weeks now.

i notice i drew a lot of background this year , more than i usually do which is fun to look at! but the asriel train is still going strong LMAO . i think ive improved a little bit from last year maybe, not as much as i want to tho <w<;;; oof.

and again, thank yall for those who are still sticking around to see my mess of a doodle lmao. inconsistent uploads and a lot of t e xt  po s t. im sorry bout that haha. as always i hope yall stick around as see where this goes!


or maybe not go since theres is a big thanos potential looming AHAHAHA

Thanks yall for the fun 2018~
